{"tid":2403770,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"杜汶澤宣佈《721誰主真相》編導蔡玉玲加盟「喱騷」擲500萬改善網絡攻手機App","createTime":"2021-02-11T09:35:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T10:22:54.000Z","uid":262724,"like":202,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"bec345636b81553ca59ec2815c5adbc294cb5ba9","tid":2403770,"uid":262724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-11T09:35:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/3Bq8WUaX4kU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F3Bq8WUaX4kU&d=i0%2FHWd2N8RLCa1A1b4xPLJB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=c3a34edb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/3Bq8WUaX4kU</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jMQ_J0Q_VPrer-WFFpkG5aKPvdk=/1024x576/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DZOJADYCYZCDZKE2V42B6NDQAI.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FjMQ_J0Q_VPrer-WFFpkG5aKPvdk%3D%2F1024x576%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDZOJADYCYZCDZKE2V42B6NDQAI.jpeg&h=c973770b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n杜汶澤去年12月把2018年於社交平台建立、擁超過100萬人follow的「杜汶澤喱騷 Chapman To&rsquo;s Late Show」撤出FACEBOOK及YouTube，成立會員制「喱騷」平台，雖然平台建立初期，出現不同技術問題要改善，幸得網民力撐，入會人數越來越多。大年初一前夕，阿澤今日在社交平台上載宣傳片，為平台今年做一個簡單節目巡禮，透露平台已投放500萬元進行改善網絡程之餘，同時宣佈《鏗鏘集：721誰主真相》編導蔡玉玲加盟「喱騷」，以及平台即將在AppleStore及Google Pay上架。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港台《鏗鏘集》編導<span class=\"red\">蔡玉玲</span>去年11月遭警方上門拘捕，被控「為取得道路交通條例下的證明書而作出虛假陳述」，港台節目製作人員工會指，管理層以有關案件進入司法程序為由，去年11月起停止蔡玉玲參與《鏗鏘集》節目製作。阿澤今日接受《蘋果》電話訪問，問到蔡玉玲加盟平台以及斥500萬改善網絡工程一事，他表示：「係呀，係呀，而家好多讀者支持，所以財政都叫穩健，之前用咗500萬改善網絡工程。所以會有新節目，仲會有節目巡禮。請咗蔡玉玲、導演<span class=\"red\">黃秋生</span>做嘅真人騷。聽聞佢（蔡玉玲）拍完《721誰主真相》之後工作量同之前有好大分別，而我哋一直欠缺資料搜集好叻嘅人，而佢喺呢方面好出色，同佢合作係by project free lance形式。同埋買咗<span class=\"red\">《達明一派》演唱會</span>獨家播映權。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n阿澤續指：「<span class=\"red\">林子穎</span>幫我哋拍嘅第一部劇集，卡士噚日都已經定好晒，除咗有我哋一哥<span class=\"red\">王宗堯</span>，同埋黃到金嘅<span class=\"red\">李綺雯</span>，會拍一部愛情動作實況喜劇，過年喇，祝大家新年快樂，咁大家與其安心出行，不如開心入會喇，大家睇節目睇得開心啲。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/v535bcEOh7g0-GS7yE9hmlt4YTc=/2044x1184/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/HRAZSMZNKZGSVCDQ2GL4IK72NI.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fv535bcEOh7g0-GS7yE9hmlt4YTc%3D%2F2044x1184%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FHRAZSMZNKZGSVCDQ2GL4IK72NI.png&h=ada1862a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/lwhq0XRR1NctPYUd3byo42myf7k=/2274x1440/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/UFTEICYX6ZHBRIUYG447BTJDAI.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Flwhq0XRR1NctPYUd3byo42myf7k%3D%2F2274x1440%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FUFTEICYX6ZHBRIUYG447BTJDAI.png&h=8d9737f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/6tqf1WnsDYVjVI4EeJTLvDC812k=/2268x1184/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/2VTGETWQKJADPA5ZE2NMPF3I3U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6tqf1WnsDYVjVI4EeJTLvDC812k%3D%2F2268x1184%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F2VTGETWQKJADPA5ZE2NMPF3I3U.png&h=fd2cdcc0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/pfNL1F9Zjtyb1unTSrel4n6jXyo=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PHFPIF5MOVEHDBUGLKFZTOLHL4.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FpfNL1F9Zjtyb1unTSrel4n6jXyo%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfr